      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute favorite ride. She\u2019s been such a joy to own\u2014honest, reliable, and always puts a smile on my face when I turn the key. I\u2019ve taken great care of her over the years, and while she\u2019s seen a few miles of happy memories (with just a couple of tiny beauty marks to show for it), she still drives like a dream and looks fantastic in the driveway. I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate her as much as I have. Come on over, grab a coffee, and let\u2019s see if she\u2019s the one for you!",
