      "description": "This is a meticulously sorted example for the serious driver. It features a Stage 1 ECU remap for optimized torque curves and a short-throw shifter that offers bolt-action precision. I\u2019ve addressed the common weak points with a high-flow aluminum radiator and reinforced subframe bushings to enhance chassis rigidity. The Torsen limited-slip differential ensures maximum traction through the corners, while the suspension geometry has been dialed in for aggressive turn-in. Maintenance has been proactive, not reactive, utilizing high-zinc synthetics to protect the valvetrain. If you value mechanical sympathy and peak power-to-weight ratios, this setup is ready for the canyon or the track.",
      "price": 38500.0,
